## Pro Features

Pro features (marked with "PRO" badge in the application) require a commercial
license. See https://polar.sh/AllTheMachines for licensing options.

Pro features include but are not limited to:
- Professional Meters (VU, PPM, RMS, LUFS, True Peak, K-System)
- Visualizations (Spectrum Analyzer, Spectrogram, Goniometer, Vectorscope)
- Interactive Curves (EQ, Compressor, Envelope, LFO, Filter Response)
- Specialized Audio Elements (Piano, Drum Pads, Step Sequencer, XY Pad)
- Asset Library and Custom SVG Management
- Custom Knob Styles
